 layers of viscoelastic memory foam which are then wrapped in three layers of polyurethane memory foam. The end result is long-lasting durability in addition to very responsive support levels.","The Luxury Grand 14” comes with a mattress cover meant to provide both a practical and aesthetic purpose. The cover is made up of a satin-like material combined with a gold-enhanced soft knit top and gold braiding around the edges. The end result is a very elegant and luxurious appearance.","The SilverRest Sleep Shop Luxury Grand 14” could be the best memory foam mattress for you due to SilverRest’s dedication to creating a uniquely supportive and comfortable sleeping experience. Their efforts at creating a multi-layered mattress that exceeds the design of most other mattresses makes this a perfect purchase."]},"id":"9995f39e-e377-419a-b51a-b2b5e5c1ebb6","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_56792","url":"/silverrest-sleep-shop-luxury-grand-mattress-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-06-19T11:35:35Z","datePublished":"2013-06-19T11:35:35Z","name":"SilverRest Luxury Grand","synopsis":"The SilverRest Sleep Shop Luxury Grand 14” has a unique claim to fame – it was designed with NASA technology. Aiming this best memory foam mattress at consumers who toss and turn all night, SilverRest addresses countless support and comfort problems with its incredibly thick memory foam bed.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"The SilverRest Sleep Shop Luxury Grand 14” has a unique claim to fame – it was designed with NASA technology. Aiming this best memory foam mattress at consumers who toss and turn all night, SilverRest addresses countless